data.description: Amongst the tall towering pine trees on a park-like half acre lot, sits this well maintained and stylishly updated home! Living in Chester means you'll never face a shortage of activities to get out and enjoy with many historical sites, parks, restaurants and entertainment nearby to explore. Step inside and find so much to love with plenty of space for everyone to spread out or come together and gather in the family room with a warming stone fireplace. Relax and unwind in the 3 Season Sunroom with panoramic views of the huge private back yard. Create masterful cuisine with a central Kitchen that fills the heart of the home with all new appliances and stylish finishes. The spacious primary bedroom is complete with a full en-suite bath & large Walk in Closet making it a perfect owners retreat. Recent updates enhancing the overall appeal and functionality of the property include new water heater, new HVAC, new fencing, new toilets, new fixtures, new appliances & more. Outdoor living is easy with fully fenced backyard, tons of parking in the driveway and an oversized two-car garage that also provides room for all your toys or hobbies. Make this your dream home – where comfort, style, and functionality seamlessly come together. Perfect for Anyone, Perfect for you!
